cleaned_text: Duplicate Forms If at any time you need additional and/or duplicate application forms, you will need to [log into your profile](https://services.kbml.ky.gov/ebusiness/Login.aspx?mode=login) and access the instructions/forms. This is the only way to obtain these forms. Email Address Board communications are predominantly sent via email. Please ensure that emails from @ky.gov do not go to your Junk/Spam folder. To update your email information at any time, [visit this page](/Pages/address.aspx) and follow the instructions.
